# 📐 Flexbox Layout Practice

A CSS project built while learning Flexbox — covers basic page layout with a navbar and text content arranged using CSS Flexbox properties.

🔗 **Live Demo:** [singular-beijinho-5917be.netlify.app](https://singular-beijinho-5917be.netlify.app)

---

## 📌 About

This project practices core Flexbox concepts:
- Creating a horizontal navigation bar with `display: flex`
- Controlling layout direction, alignment, and spacing
- Structuring a basic page layout using Flexbox

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox)

